HEADWORD: Polyonym
<hw>Pol"y*o*nym</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
object which has a variety of names.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A polynomial name or term.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polyonymous</ent>⟦br⟧
